reviews.text: The architecture is amazing - undoubtedly one of the greet Victorian stations. It could really do with some investment in the concourse and food/drink offer but well worth a look if you're in the city.
Great station I only put 4 starts as many times I have been here there are all ways police riot vans out side what is a bit strange oh but it’s great connection to platforms
The station building is a work of art. I just wanted to spend time taking photos but my wife said we are here to look at the town and not the station. Well worth a little trip for some photos
York has always had some friendly staff. Trouble is when you have only a few minutes to get from Platform 1 to Platform 9 it doesnt allow you much wiggle room. Though still an amazing station.
Easy to negotiate and clear announcements.  Toilets not too clean on platform 9.
